1
00:00:02,887 --> 00:00:07,899
笙ｪDo you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string笙ｪ

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:12,499
笙ｪTied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade笙ｪ

3
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,999
笙ｪBy your side once笙ｪ

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,074
笙ｪI laughed with the world
wild and free笙ｪ

5
00:00:17,075 --> 00:00:21,049
笙ｪYet now there's no one
to carry the story on笙ｪ

6
00:00:21,050 --> 00:00:25,970
笙ｪDo you know you are the one string
woven through my fate笙ｪ

7
00:00:25,987 --> 00:00:30,699
笙ｪCoiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line笙ｪ

8
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:35,261
笙ｪIf love is meant to fall
more wretched the fiercer its flight笙ｪ

9
00:00:35,262 --> 00:00:40,445
笙ｪYet I still came to answer your call笙ｪ

10
00:00:40,725 --> 00:00:43,124
=Shall We Dance=

11
00:00:43,125 --> 00:00:46,157
=Episode 21=

12
00:00:51,187 --> 00:00:54,300
(I once had a dream.)

13
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:59,420
(A dream that filled me with dread.)

14
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:18,300
(Could it be that today窶ｦ)

15
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:25,700
(is the day this dream comes true?)

16
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,220
Come with me.

17
00:01:38,580 --> 00:01:39,700
Chu Ying.

18
00:01:40,775 --> 00:01:41,895
Chu Ying.

19
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:45,300
Chu Ying.

20
00:01:47,775 --> 00:01:48,895
Chu Ying.

21
00:01:51,620 --> 00:01:54,100
You're awake. How do you feel?

22
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:59,260
Have you gone daft?

23
00:01:59,700 --> 00:02:00,820
This isn't a dream.

24
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,740
What a surprise.

25
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:11,140
You gave me quite a fright last night.

26
00:02:11,512 --> 00:02:13,392
I thought that nightmare had come true.

27
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:32,095
It's so quiet.

28
00:02:32,740 --> 00:02:33,900
It's beautiful here.

29
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,660
Where is this place?

30
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:36,619
This is a lake

31
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:38,580
a few li outside the capital.

32
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:40,620
The terrain nearby is complex.

33
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:42,300
The rebels can't track us here.

34
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,380
Nor will it be easy for you to leave.

35
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:46,580
What?

36
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,460
Afraid I might run off?

37
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,820
You won't let the rebels
overrun the capital.

38
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,300
And I won't let you leave either.

39
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:56,860
I have a question.

40
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,780
Jia Yi and Sun Gong
are plotting rebellion.

41
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,259
I assume the invasion

42
00:03:01,260 --> 00:03:02,419
and this palace coup

43
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:04,140
are orchestrated by them.

44
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:07,500
I've been investigating them in secret.

45
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:10,060
They're connected to the Zhen clan case.

46
00:03:11,620 --> 00:03:12,740
I believe

47
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,059
Sun Gong is actually

48
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:15,780
Zhen Muyu,
who vanished twenty years ago.

49
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:16,739
And

50
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,220
he calls Jia Yi "Uncle."

51
00:03:19,220 --> 00:03:20,820
Uncle is an illegitimate son,

52
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:23,220
so he's not truly tied to the Zhen clan.

53
00:03:23,525 --> 00:03:24,245
However,

54
00:03:24,650 --> 00:03:27,130
Father and Mother treated him
very well since childhood.

55
00:03:27,180 --> 00:03:29,750
An elder brother is like a father,
and his wife like a mother.

56
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:31,700
In his heart,

57
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:34,180
they mattered more than his own parents.

58
00:03:34,487 --> 00:03:37,657
So they're your brother and your uncle.

59
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,779
I've secretly tried

60
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:44,259
to stop Uncle and my brother

61
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,820
from colluding with foreign forces,

62
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:48,260
to prevent tragedy.

63
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,860
But their resentment runs too deep.

64
00:03:51,087 --> 00:03:52,487
I couldn't turn things around.

65
00:03:53,100 --> 00:03:54,780
I had no choice but this last resort.

66
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,620
You should've told me sooner.

67
00:03:57,500 --> 00:03:58,820
If I had,

68
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:00,579
back when you doubted

69
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:02,140
my purpose for returning,

70
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,020
what would you have done?

71
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:06,019
I would've joined forces with Aunt,

72
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,700
killed the two of them,

73
00:04:08,260 --> 00:04:09,939
then placed you under house arrest

74
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:11,180
to eliminate any risks.

75
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:14,740
Just as I expected.

76
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:17,340
So I allowed myself one selfish choice.

77
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:20,459
But things are different now.

78
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:22,820
After learning
the full story behind this case,

79
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,660
I can't bring myself to kill them.

80
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,859
I, Chu Ying,
have always put the state first.

81
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:29,740
This time, I'll be selfish too.

82
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:32,540
I haven't told anyone.

83
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:35,020
Even my aunt is still in the dark.

84
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:36,499
Trust me.

85
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:39,380
I'll do everything I can
to resolve this feud.

86
00:04:39,962 --> 00:04:41,082
Thank you.

87
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:47,620
I have another question.

88
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:51,440
Your brother is my uncle-in-law.

89
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,460
Doesn't that mean you're my elder?

90
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:55,420
Indeed.

91
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:58,100
That would make me your aunt.

92
00:04:58,940 --> 00:05:00,100
I won't allow that.

93
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:02,499
You can only be my one and only...

94
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,540
Enough.

95
00:05:04,712 --> 00:05:06,019
At a time like this,

96
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,260
it isn't appropriate.

97
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:12,099
I have another question.

98
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,140
Why were you in the hall?

99
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:20,020
I couldn't bear to see
someone dear to me

100
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:21,540
fight to the death.

101
00:05:36,620 --> 00:05:39,220
You didn't want to lose me, did you?

102
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,100
Chu Ying.

103
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:48,820
Last night,
I didn't go there to save you.

104
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,260
I know.

105
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:52,220
Jia Yi must've sent you to capture me.

106
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:55,460
I defied my uncle's orders
and saved you.

107
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,700
I meant to take you far away,

108
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:59,140
away from this blood feud.

109
00:05:59,420 --> 00:06:01,300
I'd find us
a distant mountain near a river

110
00:06:01,380 --> 00:06:02,660
and spend our lives there.

111
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:04,299
In those distant hills and rivers,

112
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,859
I'd farm, you'd weave,

113
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:08,900
and we'd raise a son and a daughter.
Wouldn't that be bliss?

114
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:10,980
What do you say?

115
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:12,380
Of course I'd want that.

116
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,940
But I can't promise you.

117
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,340
Xiao Man,

118
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:21,500
as Chu Ying,

119
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:23,099
I'd gladly cast everything aside

120
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:25,380
to live an unshackled life with you.

121
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:28,899
But as an emperor,

122
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,420
as the ruler of this realm,

123
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,140
I must stand
with the land and its people.

124
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:35,540
The capital is in grave danger now.

125
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:37,659
Your elite forces are
all reinforcing the borders.

126
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:39,059
How will you stand against my uncle?

127
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:40,499
As long as we stay together...

128
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:41,660
Enough.

129
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:45,380
If I could abandon
my uncle and my brother,

130
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:47,740
I wouldn't have
suffered all these years,

131
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:50,300
nor would I have brought you here.

132
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,220
Xiao Man,

133
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:54,020
we're both exhausted.

134
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:57,870
Get some rest.

135
00:06:58,980 --> 00:07:00,260
Let me think.

136
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:02,940
Come.

137
00:08:57,740 --> 00:08:58,860
Stop right there.

138
00:09:03,050 --> 00:09:05,410
So you've made up your mind to leave.

139
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,624
Yes.

140
00:09:06,625 --> 00:09:08,705
No matter what, I must face this.

141
00:09:09,462 --> 00:09:11,699
My uncle originally
planned to capture you alive,

142
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:13,900
then have you executed
before the rebel army.

143
00:09:14,687 --> 00:09:16,124
This force here

144
00:09:16,125 --> 00:09:17,999
was former soldiers of the Xiao Army.

145
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,120
I know.

146
00:09:19,412 --> 00:09:21,131
They've been waiting for your return

147
00:09:21,132 --> 00:09:22,499
to use your flesh and blood

148
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,339
to appease my mother's soul.

149
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:26,060
If that is truly the case,

150
00:09:27,425 --> 00:09:29,905
then this is my destiny.

151
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:39,300
Chu Ying.

152
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:42,139
I'm torn between you
and my own kin.

153
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:43,619
Can you understand how I feel?

154
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,100
Of course I can.

155
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:47,700
Then for my sake,

156
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,620
will you yield?

157
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:51,236
This is something I must face

158
00:09:51,237 --> 00:09:53,195
as a descendant of the Chu clan.

159
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:59,900
I can't let the moment
I fear most come to pass.

160
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:02,300
I will never let you

161
00:10:02,637 --> 00:10:04,597
walk toward your own death.

162
00:10:07,025 --> 00:10:09,705
All this tragedy was
caused by my father.

163
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:11,739
I believe I owe

164
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,220
the Zhen clan justice.

165
00:10:22,940 --> 00:10:23,659
If the blood in me

166
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:26,140
that belongs to the Chu lineage
were to run dry,

167
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:28,980
would we return
to how we were as children?

168
00:10:32,450 --> 00:10:33,570
Xiao Man.

169
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:34,899
Once I leave,

170
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:36,940
I may never see you again.

171
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,700
Before I go,

172
00:10:39,037 --> 00:10:41,597
will you dance with me?

173
00:11:27,850 --> 00:11:31,770
笙ｪI wanted to ask you
the meaning of forever笙ｪ

174
00:11:32,175 --> 00:11:35,295
笙ｪIs it longing that never rests笙ｪ

175
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:39,207
笙ｪLove that echoes without end笙ｪ

176
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:44,095
笙ｪOr promises that can't be kept笙ｪ

177
00:11:46,050 --> 00:11:49,470
笙ｪAll those vows of forever we made笙ｪ

178
00:11:50,012 --> 00:11:53,457
笙ｪAre sealed away in darkness now笙ｪ

179
00:11:55,250 --> 00:11:58,057
笙ｪHow cruel笙ｪ

180
00:11:58,175 --> 00:12:02,332
笙ｪLove blooms and withers笙ｪ

181
00:12:04,525 --> 00:12:08,607
笙ｪThe more I try to forget
the fiercer the love burns笙ｪ

182
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:12,995
笙ｪThe more I retreat
the sharper it feels笙ｪ

183
00:12:13,362 --> 00:12:16,674
笙ｪHow am I supposed to let go笙ｪ

184
00:12:16,675 --> 00:12:20,757
笙ｪAnd bring this story to an end笙ｪ

185
00:12:22,675 --> 00:12:26,282
笙ｪAfter ten thousand years
adrift in the mortal world笙ｪ

186
00:12:26,675 --> 00:12:30,820
笙ｪWhy is my wish still unfulfilled笙ｪ

187
00:12:30,887 --> 00:12:39,620
笙ｪHow absurd that
this longing just won't die笙ｪ

188
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:42,220
Are you set on risking your life?

189
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:44,380
If I don't face this,

190
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:46,860
neither of us will ever live in peace.

191
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,420
Don't worry.

192
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:51,260
I'm going back to resolve the hatred.

193
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,420
Xiao Man,

194
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:54,540
come back with me.

195
00:12:55,860 --> 00:12:57,100
I can't.

196
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,819
I don't want to
face someone important to me

197
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:00,819
in a fight to the death.

198
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:01,540
I...

199
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:03,460
Enough.

200
00:13:03,525 --> 00:13:04,645
I understand.

201
00:13:07,140 --> 00:13:08,380
Don't go.

202
00:13:10,512 --> 00:13:12,272
When everything is settled,

203
00:13:13,650 --> 00:13:15,370
I'll still be waiting for your return.

204
00:13:34,975 --> 00:13:38,582
笙ｪAfter ten thousand years
adrift in the mortal world笙ｪ

205
00:13:38,975 --> 00:13:43,120
笙ｪWhy is my wish still unfulfilled笙ｪ

206
00:13:43,187 --> 00:13:51,849
笙ｪHow absurd that
this longing just won't die笙ｪ

207
00:13:51,850 --> 00:13:56,862
笙ｪDo you know, our fingertips
are bound by one string笙ｪ

208
00:13:56,863 --> 00:14:01,462
笙ｪTied to an attachment
that blooms only to fade笙ｪ

209
00:14:01,463 --> 00:14:02,962
笙ｪBy your side once笙ｪ

210
00:14:02,963 --> 00:14:06,037
笙ｪI laughed with the world
wild and free笙ｪ

211
00:14:06,038 --> 00:14:09,219
笙ｪYet now there's no one
to carry the story on笙ｪ

212
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:10,779
Chu Ying.

213
00:14:10,780 --> 00:14:14,949
笙ｪDo you know you are the one string
woven through my fate笙ｪ

214
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:19,339
笙ｪCoiled through the years,
where longing sharpens into pain's line笙ｪ

215
00:14:19,340 --> 00:14:21,579
We'll both go back

216
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:24,060
and face our destiny.

217
00:14:24,225 --> 00:14:30,920
笙ｪYet I still came to answer your call笙ｪ

218
00:14:47,475 --> 00:14:51,082
笙ｪAfter ten thousand years
adrift in the mortal world笙ｪ

219
00:14:51,475 --> 00:14:55,620
笙ｪWhy is my wish still unfulfilled笙ｪ

220
00:14:55,687 --> 00:15:04,349
笙ｪHow absurd that
this longing just won't die笙ｪ

221
00:15:04,350 --> 00:15:09,362
笙ｪDo you know, our fingertips
